OL,7,FA captain accused of causing the fatal
OL,8,FNorth Sea tanker crash waited until
OL,9,Fthe other vessel was only one nautical
OL,10,Fmile away before trying to change
OL,11,Fcourse, a court has heard.
OL,13,FVladimir Motin was captaining the
OL,14,FSolong when it hit the anchored US oil
OL,15,Ftanker, the Stena Immaculate, close to
OL,16,Fthe Humber Estuary on 10 March last
OL,17,Fyear.
