OL,7,FA fuel leak ignited and engulfed both
OL,8,Fships in flames. The body of 38-year-
OL,9,Fold Filipino Mark Angelo Pernia - who
OL,10,Fwas a crew member on the Solong - was
OL,11,Fnever found.
OL,13,FRussian national Motin is accused of
OL,14,Fmanslaughter over Mr Pernia's death,
OL,15,Fwith a trial at the Old Bailey hearing
OL,16,Fhe was on sole watch duty of the
OL,17,Fvessel which was travelling at 16
OL,18,Fknots (18mph) at the time of the
OL,19,Fallision.
