OL,7,FMotin would have been aware the Stena
OL,8,Fwas in its direct path from at least
OL,9,Fnine nautical miles away through a
OL,10,Fradar, his defence barrister James
OL,11,FLeonard KC told the London jury.
OL,13,FMr Leonard also said the ship had been
OL,14,Fon autopilot at the time. He said the
OL,15,FStena then would have come into view
OL,16,Ffrom around three nautical miles away.
