OL,3,CCaptain waited until tanker was a mile
OL,4,Caway before changing course, court
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FHe told the jury: "The defendant will
OL,8,Fsay that when he was approximately one
OL,9,Fnautical mile away from the Stena
OL,10,FImmaculate's position, he tried to
OL,11,Ftake the Solong out of autopilot so as
OL,12,Fto attempt to change course to
OL,13,Fstarboard manually, passing to the
OL,14,FStena Immaculate's stern.
OL,16,F"There is no dispute that had he
OL,17,Fchanged course in the way he intended,
OL,18,Fthere would have been no collision.
OL,26,@oD@SOUxD@AOU
