OL,3,CCaptain waited until tanker was a mile
OL,4,Caway before changing course, court
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,F"That attempt was not successful and
OL,8,Fthe Solong did not change course at
OL,9,Fall."
OL,11,FThe defence instead say the jury
OL,12,Fneeded to consider whether it was
OL,13,F"reasonable" to wait until the vessels
OL,14,Fwere a mile apart before averting, and
OL,15,Fwhat he should have done in the time
OL,16,Fbetween spotting the Stena on the
OL,17,Fradar and when it came into vision.
