OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FMr Leonard also invited the jury to
OL,8,Fthink about what Motin should have
OL,9,Fdone at the point when the Stena was
OL,10,Fthree miles away.
OL,12,FThe court heard on Tuesday 13 January
OL,13,Fthat the crash and Mr Pernia's death
OL,14,Fhad been "entirely avoidable".
OL,16,FProsecuting barrister Tom Little KC
OL,17,Fsaid Motin had done "absolutely
OL,18,Fnothing" to prevent the Solong from
OL,19,Fhitting the Stena.
