OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FIt was also heard the Motin abandoned
OL,8,Fship shortly after the crash, leaving
OL,9,Fthe bridge via a ladder.
OL,11,FThe Solong had 14 crew members and at
OL,12,Fthe time was carrying mainly alcoholic
OL,13,Fspirits and a few hazardous
OL,14,Fsubstances, including empty but
OL,15,Funclean sodium cyanide containers.
OL,17,FIt had departed Grangemouth in
OL,18,FScotland the day before and was bound
OL,19,Ffor Rotterdam when it hit the other
OL,20,Fvessel.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/8
